        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg">
          Test continuous monitoring of simulated vital signs and dialysis parameters. We use a mock server to
          generate data and test anomaly detection before they become emergencies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
        <div class="bg-orange-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
