          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Nocturnal Safety</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg">
          Specialized monitoring for overnight treatments when patients are most vulnerable and least likely to notice
          problems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
        <div class="bg-teal-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
