        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Device Simulation & Integration Preview</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg">
          Currently connects to our mock IoT server for data simulation. We are optimizing the core architecture for
          seamless future integration with home dialysis equipment and EHR systems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
        <div class="bg-fuchsia-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-fuchsia-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
