          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Treatment Analytics</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg">
          Detailed reporting and trend analysis to help providers optimize treatment plans and identify potential issues
          early.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

