                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Preview: Architecture compatible with wearables and any data streaming health device
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              Simple setup for mock server connection
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8">
        <div class="shrink-0 relative z-10">
          <div
            class="bg-emerald-700 text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold shadow-lg">
            3
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Start Simulation and Test Alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Begin your simulated session. Our system will send mock data to test the anomaly detection logic and
